" PURPOSE:
" 	Check that the passed argument validates to true
" ARGUMENTS:
" 	arg1: Should validate to TRUE() == (1==1)
" 	... : Optional message placeholder.
" RETURNS:
" 	TRUE() if true and
" 	FALSE() if false
" ---------------------------------------------------------------------
